snippet.title: Tropico 4 US E3 2011 Trailer
snippet.description: This is the E3 2011 trailer for Tropico 4, the upcoming simulation sequel by Haemimont Games and Kalypso Media for PC and Xbox 360. Continue your reign as El Presidente in August 2011!
